Mr. Lu,

13
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:03,440
luckily, it wasn't fatal.

14
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,800
You can recover soon.

15
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,800
Lu, I'm begging you.

16
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,200
Can you stop terrifying me?

17
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,360
The circumstances demand.

18
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,360
Last time you took a bullet,

19
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,520
you said so.

20
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:20,480
It's been a few days.

21
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,760
I'll buy you time at the office,

22
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,920
but not for long.

23
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,160
As for Director He,

24
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:31,200
you'll explain yourself.

25
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,080
Lu Ye.

26
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:49,440
Why stand so far away?

27
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,000
Standing there,

28
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,240
how can I hug you?

29
00:01:59,603 --> 00:02:04,670
♪Watching the hour hand in slow motion♪

30
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,280
Don't cry.

31
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:10,120
♪The minute hand follows like a shadow♪

32
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,560
It's fine. It doesn't hurt.

33
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,160
Lu Ye.

34
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,520
If you die,

35
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,240
I won't wait for you.

36
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:18,840
♪Just like us♪

37
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,680
I know.

38
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,920
I won't visit your grave either.

39
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,040
I know.

40
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:27,520
All vows and sweet promises

41
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,520
only matter when you're alive.

42
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,840
Only fools remain faithful.

43
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,800
Many men will pursue me.

44
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,880
Someone as selfish as me

45
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,280
will definitely find another man.

46
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,360
I'll amass wealth

47
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,960
and forget you completely.

48
00:02:40,724 --> 00:02:45,651
♪Backing up intimacy as cold data♪

49
00:02:46,227 --> 00:02:47,067
I know.

50
